### Versions

The following table shows the Netbox and Proxmox versions compatible
(tested) with Proxbox plugin.

| netbox version        | proxmox version          | proxbox version
| ------------- |-------------|-------------|
| >= v3.2.0 | >= v6.2.0 | =v0.0.4
| >= v3.0.0 < v3.2| >= v6.2.0 | =v0.0.3

